text: Tammy Heydenrych (born 1980) is a South African water polo player. She played at the 2009 World Aquatics Championships. and 2009 Women's Water Polo World League. == References == == Other websites == * South African captain Tammy Heydenrych (R) tries to score against Australian Brionwen Knox during the water-polo preliminary round Group B match Australia vs. South Africa on July 21, 2009 at the FINA World Swimming Championships in Rome.
